    "In the absence of information to demonstrate otherwise, the proposed takeaway use, by reason of noise and disturbance caused by customers entering and leaving the premises, vehicles parking and manoeuvring, particularly during the evening hours of operation, would be detrimental to the amenities of the occupiers of nearby residential properties, contrary to Havering Local Plan Policies 7 and 34, and London Plan (2021) policies D14 and T7.",
